OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSocial care: Half a million
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fadults waiting for help in 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FEngland                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of adults waiting for social
OL,6, care in England has risen sharply to   
OL,7, more than 500,000, according to        
OL,8, estimates by social work bosses.       
OL,10,FSimilar research last year put the     
OL,11,Ffigure at about 294,000, says the      
OL,12,FAssociation of Directors of Adult      
OL,13,FSocial Services (Adass).               
OL,15,F"We're seeing a devastating impact on  
OL,16,Fpeople's lives," said Adass president  
OL,17,FSarah McClinton.                       
OL,19,FThe government says reforming social   
OL,20,Fcare is a priority.                    
